" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Mitral stenosis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 261px; height: 189px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    M-mode echocardiogram of severe mitral stenosis shows concordant motion of anterior and posterior mitral valve (MV) leaflets which are thickened. The E-F slope is flat, resulting from very elevated left atrial pressure throughout diastole, suggesting a marked gradient across the mitral valve.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Provided by Thomas Binder, MD, et al. Interactive Echocardiography. A Clinical Atlas. Futura, 1997.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
