"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Effects of endoscopic sclerotherapy (EST) and transjugular intrahepatic portosystemic shunt (TIPS) on variceal rebleeding rates in published clinical trials of secondary prevention of variceal hemorrhage. All but the last trial showed a significantly lower rate of rebleeding with TIPS.",
